{"tid":773834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國2020年前組建太空軍","createTime":"2018-08-10T00:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T02:31:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a526c46d6d3782cfadbabe8ccbb2eb5237966a","tid":773834,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T00:47:41.000Z","msg":"美國2020年前組建太空軍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180810/s00014/1533839408008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180810%2Fs00014%2F1533839408008&d=HmHxKdJjUk%2BEk7gZk2GpEdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=2acda20f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180810%2Fs00014%2F1533839408008&h=df5f2905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180810/s00014/1533839408008</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】美國副總統彭斯昨公布建立太空部隊的細節，稱希望在2020年前建立美軍第6兵種「太空軍」。他表示現在正尋求國會支持總統特朗普的太空軍計劃。他昨在國防部發表演說，說：「美國單單在太空有一席位並不足夠，必須在太空保持優勢。」他稱特朗普政府將會促國會未來5年撥款80億美元建軍。特朗普今年3月首次提出設立太空軍的構思，到6月下令設立，但現時主管太空事務的空軍對設立太空軍仍有抗拒。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社）"},{"pid":"18c5f8fb0034b437ccbd7729c28dba705629e5d0","tid":773834,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T00:51:28.000Z","msg":"2025 2025 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2025</span></span>"},{"pid":"710423f2edb392c2b4bc0c652f22504befb85d3f","tid":773834,"uid":67325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T02:31:54.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得似星球大戰計劃d朋友？"}]}